      "instruction": "<p>Reboil half a kettle</p><p>Chop your<strong> cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Peel and finely slice (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]<strong> </span>boiled water</strong>, then add<strong> </strong>your<strong> soft cheese </strong>and mix well – this is your<strong> creamy vegetable stock</strong></p>",
