      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>halved cherry tomatoes </strong>and the <strong>sliced garlic </strong>to the pan and cook for 1-2 min or until starting to soften</p>",
