      "instruction": "<p>Once the tomatoes are tender, add the <strong>basa</strong> and <strong>spinach</strong>, and cook, covered, for 4-5 min further or until the basa is cooked through and the spinach has wilted – this is your <strong>creamy tomato sauce</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? Do this in batches!</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
